      "description": "urnetwork_connect_contract_failures_total \u2014 the lossless counter behind the sampled contract-error log exemplars. missing_companion_origin climbing while everything else is healthy = stale provider selection serving zombies (playbook 5.9; post-churn variant 5.9.7). insufficient_balance step-change = netEscrow drift re-emerging (\u00a74). Empty until the instrumented api build deploys."
