          },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({env=\"$env\"} |~ `connect: connection refused` [1m]))",
          "refId": "B",
          "legendFormat": "connection-refused (page >10/min)"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "warp-loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({env=\"$env\"} |~ `CLUSTERDOWN` [1m]))",
          "refId": "C",
          "legendFormat": "clusterdown (page >5/min)"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "warp-loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({env=\"$env\"} |~ `OOM command not allowed` [1m]))",
          "refId": "D",
          "legendFormat": "oom-writes (page >1/min)"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "warp-loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({env=\"$env\"} |~ `panic:|goroutine [0-9]+ \\[` [1m]))",
          "refId": "E",
          "legendFormat": "panic (page >5/min)"
        }
      ],
      "description": "First-match taxonomy from the monitor tailers. dial-io-timeout = accept-path starvation (5.2); connection-refused = process dead / wrong interface (5.2); clusterdown = slot coverage lost (5.3); oom-writes = node at maxmemory, writes fail while reads work (5.4); panic = read the innermost app frame."
